        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 116:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and Kal ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 69:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", after the Aramaic style, although it is not unhebraic). Righteous is Jahve - this is an universal truth, which has been verified in the present circumstances; - He hath cut asunder the cords of the wicked (עבות as in ",
        "children": []
